: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 0.8em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">\n     <span leaf=\"\">模型一览</span>\n    </figcaption>\n   </figure>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">以及，IQuest-Coder 系列有三个变体：</span><span leaf=\"\">Instruct/</span><span leaf=\"\">Thinking/</span><span leaf=\"\">Loop</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">别的没啥，不过有个值得说的&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(198, 110, 73);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Code-Flow 训练</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">IQuest-Coder 从代码仓库的演化、commit和重构轨迹中学习，把代码当时间序列数据</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">思路....颇有搞量化的味道</span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-size: 19.5px;font-weight: bold;margin: 4em auto 2em;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;display: table;padding: 0.3em 1em;background: rgb(198, 110, 73);border-radius: 8px;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 4px 6px;color: white !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">争议</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">发布当天，GitHub 上就有人开了个 Issue：</